  "ciliary_role": "Orthologue of Chlamydomo s PF16. Axoneme central apparatus protein, essential for sperm flagellar motility and motility of ependymal cilia, as well as mainte nce of the structural integrity of the sperm flagella by serving as a scaffold protein (12167721). Role in ciliogenesis, axoneme orientation, and cell polarity. Spag6-deficient epithelial cells in the brain and trachea lose rotatio l polarity and Spag6-eficient mice suffer hydrocephalus and are sterile because of sperm motility defects (25333478). Mutated in PCD with male infertility with severe asthenoteratospermia (32124190)",
